      • arrayMapper

        public me.zingle.api.sdk.model.ZingleList<Model> arrayMapper(org.json.JSONObject source)
                                                                                                      throws me.zingle.api.sdk.Exceptions.MappingErrorEx
        Converts JSON data from HTTP response into ZingleList (see HTTP Response in Zingle API docs). status part forms the properties of ZingleList and result forms array of objects of Model type.
        Parameters:
        source - Successfull HTTP response in form of JSON object
        Returns:
        ZingleList with Model objects and response status.
        Throws:
        me.zingle.api.sdk.Exceptions.MappingErrorEx
